edu.gmu.team1.idt2014

Interface ITestBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MainTestBuilder, NullTestBuilder

    public interface ITestBuilder
    An ITestBuilder is a utility class that makes it very easy to create a build test structures. By default, test builder assumes 1 branch per method and no note per test.
    Test builder returns itself in each method except build as this allows calls to be chained simply. for example

    TestBuilder
    .test(...)
    .test(...)
    .test(...)
    .build();
    See Also:
    MainTestBuilder, NullTestBuilder
